Multiple primary tumors in differentiated thyroid carcinoma and relationship to 
thyroid cancer outcome.

Omür O(1), Ozcan Z, Yazici B, Akgün A, Oral A, Ozkiliç H.

Author information:
(1)Ege University, Medical Faculty, Department of Nuclear Medicine, Izmir, 
