AIM: Patients with differentiated thyroid carcinoma (DTC) have long-life 
expectancy and are at risk for developing a second primary cancer. Aim of this 
study was to assess the occurrence of DTC in conjunction with other primary 
neoplasms. It was also aimed to explore the possibility of synchronous or 
